  "instructions": [
    "Heat the garlicky oil in a large tagine or Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped springy onions and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the vegetable broth, tagine spice mix, minced garlic, chopped carrots, sliced zucchini, and sliced red bell pepper.",
    "Bring to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes.",
    "Stir in the chickpeas and cook for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley."
